  <brief_title>The Prevalence and Clinical Manifestations of Human Metapneumovirus Among Children With Bronchiolitis.</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Prevalence and Clinical Manifestations of Human Metapneumovirus Among Children With Bronchiolitis in Northern Israel.</official_title>
